7:["$","main",null,{"className":"article-page","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BlogPosting\",\"headline\":\"Date Night Questions for Christian Couples Who Are Tired of \\\"How Was Your Day\\\"\",\"description\":\"Questions that move a date from logistics to connection — for dating, engaged, and married couples.\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-07-04\",\"mainEntityOfPage\":\"https://bexhearts.com/blog/date-night-questions-christian-couples\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Bexhearts\",\"url\":\"https://bexhearts.com\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Bexhearts\",\"url\":\"https://bexhearts.com\"}}"}}],["$","article",null,{"className":"article-shell","children":[["$","$L12",null,{"href":"/blog","className":"back-link","children":[["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-arrow-left","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","path","1l729n",{"d":"m12 19-7-7 7-7"}],["$","path","x3x0zl",{"d":"M19 12H5"}],"$undefined"]}],"Blog"]}],["$","header",null,{"className":"article-hero","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"section-kicker","children":"Dates"}],["$","h1",null,{"children":"Date Night Questions for Christian Couples Who Are Tired of \"How Was Your Day\""}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Questions that move a date from logistics to connection — for dating, engaged, and married couples."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"article-meta","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-07-04","children":"2026-07-04"}],["$","span",null,{"children":[4," min read"]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"article-content","children":[["$","section","0",{"children":["$undefined",[["$","p","Good questions do more for a date than a good restaurant. The goal is not interrogation; it is giving each other a reason to say something you have not said before.",{"children":"Good questions do more for a date than a good restaurant. The goal is not interrogation; it is giving each other a reason to say something you have not said before."}],["$","p","Try one of these per date, not ten: What has God been teaching you lately that you have not told me? When did you feel closest to me this month? What are you quietly worried about? What would you love us to pray for together this season?",{"children":"Try one of these per date, not ten: What has God been teaching you lately that you have not told me? When did you feel closest to me this month? What are you quietly worried about? What would you love us to pray for together this season?"}]]]}],["$","section","Match the question to the season",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Match the question to the season"}],[["$","p","Dating couples need discovery questions — story, family, faith history. Engaged couples need rhythm questions — money, conflict, church, rest. Married couples need maintenance questions — what needs repair, what deserves celebration.",{"children":"Dating couples need discovery questions — story, family, faith history. Engaged couples need rhythm questions — money, conflict, church, rest. Married couples need maintenance questions — what needs repair, what deserves celebration."}],["$","p","One honest answer is a successful date. Do not chase intensity; chase truth said gently.",{"children":"One honest answer is a successful date. Do not chase intensity; chase truth said gently."}]]]}],["$","section","Write down what you learn",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Write down what you learn"}],[["$","p","The best answers are worth keeping. A line in a shared journal — what you did, what they said, what you want to remember — turns a nice evening into part of your story.",{"children":"The best answers are worth keeping. A line in a shared journal — what you did, what they said, what you want to remember — turns a nice evening into part of your story."}],"$L13"]]}]]}],"$L14","$L15"]}]]}]
